# 5. S3 Bucket Creation

I created an S3 bucket with:

* Dynamic naming
* Common project tags

```hcl
bucket = "own-random-bucket-${random_integer.any_integer.id}"
```

### Why Random Integer?

S3 bucket names must be globally unique.

To avoid naming conflicts, I used:

```hcl
resource "random_integer" "any_integer"
```

